[font=Verdana][size=5]Introduction[/size]

Extends [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/7286]Ridgeside Village[/url] with a variety of new forage.

If today's weather is good, and yesterday's weather was also good, you can find a variety of additional flowers.

If yesterday's weather was rainy, you can find a variety of mushrooms.

If yesterday's weather was windy, perhaps some produce has blown down the ridge.

The exact forage found will depend on the weather, the location, and the date.

[size=5][b]Install[/b][/size]
[list=1]
[*]Install the latest version of [url=https://smapi.io/]SMAPI[/url].
[*]Install the latest version of [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/3231]Farm Type Manager (FTM)[/url]
[*]Install the latest version of [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/7286]Ridgeside Village[/url]
[*]Optionally install the latest version of [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/2028]PPJA - Mizu's Flowers[/url]
[*]Optionally install the latest version of [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/stardewvalley/mods/1598]PPJA - Fruits and Veggies[/url]
[*]Unzip the mod folder into [font=Courier New]Stardew Valley/Mods[/font]
[*]Run the game using SMAPI.
[/list]

